---
const title = 'Miraya Tech Labs — Design & AI Software';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="it">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2/dist/aos.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
    <style>
      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #f7f3eb;
        color: #3b2132;
        line-height: 1.7;
        font-weight: 300;
        overflow-x: hidden;
      }

      img {
        display: block;
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      button,
      input,
      textarea {
        font: inherit;
      }

      strong {
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      ::-webkit-scrollbar {
        width: 8px;
      }

      ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
        background: #f7f3eb;
      }

      ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
        background: #3b2132;
        border-radius: 10px;
      }

      body > nav {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        z-index: 50;
        padding: 1.5rem 0;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(247, 243, 235, 0.98), rgba(247, 243, 235, 0));
        transition: all 0.4s ease;
      }

      body > nav.nav-scrolled {
        background: rgba(247, 243, 235, 0.86);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(59, 33, 50, 0.08);
        padding: 1rem 0;
      }

      body > nav .max-w-7xl {
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 5rem);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2rem;
      }

      body > nav a:first-child {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        color: #3b2132;
      }

      body > nav ul {
        display: flex;
        gap: 2.5rem;
        align-items: center;
        list-style: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      body > nav li {
        margin: 0;
      }

      body > nav ul a {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        opacity: 0.75;
        transition: opacity 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
      }

      body > nav ul a:hover {
        opacity: 1;
      }

      body > nav ul a[href="#contact"] {
        background: #3b2132;
        color: #faf8f3;
        padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        opacity: 1;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
      }

      body > nav ul a[href="#contact"]:hover {
        background: #1f5867;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      main {
        padding-top: 84px;
      }

      main > section:first-of-type {
        min-height: calc(100vh - 84px);
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      main > section:first-of-type > div:first-child {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: #3b2132;
        min-height: 720px;
      }

      main > section:first-of-type > div:first-child img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        opacity: 0.8;
        transition: transform 8s ease;
      }

      main > section:first-of-type > div:first-child:hover img {
        transform: scale(1.05);
      }

      main > section:first-of-type > div:first-child > div {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 33, 50, 0.4), rgba(31, 88, 103, 0.4));
      }

      main > section:first-of-type > div:last-child {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
        position: relative;
      }

      main > section:first-of-type p:first-child {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        color: #965228;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
      }

      main > section:first-of-type h1 {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
        font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.5rem);
        line-height: 1.1;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
        max-width: 8ch;
        color: #3b2132;
      }

      main > section:first-of-type h1 em {
        font-style: normal;
        color: #1f5867;
      }

      main > section:first-of-type p:nth-of-type(2) {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        max-width: 34rem;
        opacity: 0.8;
        margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      main > section:first-of-type a[href="#contact"] {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        width: fit-content;
        background: #00a5b5;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
      }

      main > section:first-of-type a[href="#contact"]:hover {
        background: #1f5867;
        transform: translateX(6px);
      }

      #services {
        padding: 6rem 0;
        background: #faf8f3;
        position: relative;
      }

      #services .max-w-7xl,
      #vision .max-w-7xl,
      #contact .max-w-7xl,
      footer .max-w-7xl {
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 5rem);
      }

      #services .text-center {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 5rem;
      }

      #services .text-center p,
      #vision h2 em {
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      }

      #services .text-center h2,
      #vision h2,
      #contact h2 {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      }

      #services .text-center h2 {
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      }

      #services .max-w-7xl > .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
      }

      #services article {
        background: #f7f3eb;
        padding: 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 1.75rem;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
        transition: transform 0.5s ease, box-shadow 0.5s ease, border-color 0.5s ease;
      }

      #services article:hover {
        transform: translateY(-8px);
        box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(59, 33, 50, 0.12);
        border-color: rgba(130, 77, 94, 0.2);
      }

      #services article > div:first-child {
        width: 4rem;
        height: 4rem;
        border-radius: 1rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b2132, #824d5e);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: white;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      #services article p:first-of-type {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        color: #965228;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
      }

      #services article h3 {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
      }

      #services article p:last-of-type {
        margin: 0;
        opacity: 0.7;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      #vision {
        padding: 6rem 0;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      #vision .max-w-7xl {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 4rem;
        align-items: center;
      }

      #vision .relative {
        position: relative;
      }

      #vision img {
        border-radius: 1.75rem;
        box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(59, 33, 50, 0.2);
        width: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
      }

      #vision .relative > div:last-child {
        position: absolute;
        right: -1.5rem;
        bottom: -1.5rem;
        width: 12rem;
        height: 12rem;
        background: #00a5b5;
        border-radius: 999px;
        filter: blur(48px);
        opacity: 0.2;
      }

      #vision h2 {
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
        margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
      }

      #vision p {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        opacity: 0.8;
        margin: 0 0 2rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      #vision .space-y-4 {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      #vision .flex.gap-4 {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      #vision .flex.gap-4 p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        margin: 0;
        opacity: 0.8;
      }

      #contact {
        padding: 6rem 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b2132, #1f5867);
        color: #faf8f3;
      }

      #contact .max-w-7xl {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 4rem;
      }

      #contact h2 {
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
        margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
      }

      #contact p {
        margin: 0;
      }

      #contact .text-lg {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        opacity: 0.8;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        max-width: 34rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      #contact .flex.gap-8 {
        display: flex;
        gap: 2rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      #contact .flex.gap-8 p:first-child {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        opacity: 0.6;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      }

      #contact .bg-white\/5 {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        padding: 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 1.75rem;
      }

      #contact form {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }

      #contact form .grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      #contact label {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        opacity: 0.7;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      }

      #contact input,
      #contact textarea {
        width: 100%;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        border-radius: 0.85rem;
        padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
        color: #faf8f3;
        outline: none;
        transition: border-color 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
      }

      #contact input::placeholder,
      #contact textarea::placeholder {
        color: rgba(250, 248, 243, 0.6);
      }

      #contact input:focus,
      #contact textarea:focus {
        border-color: #00a5b5;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      }

      #contact button {
        width: 100%;
        border: 0;
        background: #00a5b5;
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 500;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
      }

      #contact button:hover {
        background: #965228;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      footer {
        background: #3b2132;
        color: #faf8f3;
        padding: 3rem 0;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      }

      footer .max-w-7xl {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      footer a:first-child {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      footer p {
        opacity: 0.5;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        margin: 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      footer .flex.gap-6 {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        opacity: 0.6;
      }

      footer .flex.gap-6 a:hover {
        color: #00a5b5;
      }

      @media (max-width: 1100px) {
        main > section:first-of-type,
        #vision .max-w-7xl,
        #contact .max-w-7xl,
        #services .max-w-7xl > .grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        main > section:first-of-type > div:first-child {
          min-height: 480px;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        body > nav ul {
          gap: 1rem;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
          justify-content: flex-end;
        }

        body > nav .max-w-7xl {
          align-items: flex-start;
        }

        main > section:first-of-type > div:last-child {
          padding: 2rem;
        }

        #services .max-w-7xl > .grid,
        #contact form .grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        footer .max-w-7xl {
          flex-direction: column;
          text-align: center;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-[#F7F3EB] text-[#3B2132] font-light">
    <nav id="navbar" class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 transition-all duration-400 py-6">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 flex justify-between items-center">
        <a href="#" class="text-2xl font-semibold font-serif tracking-tighter text-[#3B2132]">
          Miraya Tech Labs<span class="text-[#00A5B5]">.</span>
        </a>
        <ul class="hidden md:flex gap-10 items-center list-none">
          <li><a href="#services" class="text-sm opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">Servizi</a></li>
          <li><a href="#vision" class="text-sm opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">Visione</a></li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="#contact"
              class="bg-[#3B2132] text-[#FAF8F3] px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm transition-all hover:bg-[#1F5867] hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
              Parliamo
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
      <section class="min-h-screen grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-[#3B2132]" data-aos="fade-right">
          <img
            src="https://loremflickr.com/900/1200/architecture,detail"
            alt="Dettaglio architettonico minimalista"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-[8s]"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#3B2132]/40 to-[#1F5867]/40"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center px-8 lg:px-20 py-20 relative">
          <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#965228] font-medium mb-6">
              Sartoria Digitale &amp; Intelligenza Artificiale
            </p>
            <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-serif leading-[1.1] mb-8 text-[#3B2132]">
              L'Efficienza è un <em class="text-[#1F5867]">Arte Precisa</em>.
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg opacity-80 max-w-xl mb-12 leading-relaxed">
              Non implementiamo solo software, modelliamo processi. Fondiamo il Web Design d'avanguardia con
              l'Intelligenza Artificiale per liberare il tempo umano e ottimizzare il cuore della tua azienda.
            </p>
            <a
              href="#contact"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-[#00A5B5] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium transition-all hover:bg-[#1F5867] hover:translate-x-2 group"
            >
              Ottimizza il tuo business
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="services" class="py-24 bg-[#FAF8F3] relative">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
          <div class="text-center mb-20" data-aos="fade-up">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#965228] font-medium mb-4">Le Nostre Competenze</p>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif text-[#3B2132]">Semplificare la Complessità</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <article
              class="bg-[#F7F3EB] p-10 rounded-3xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl group border border-transparent hover:border-[#824D5E]/20"
              data-aos="fade-up"
              data-aos-delay="100"
            >
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#3B2132] to-[#824D5E] flex items-center justify-center mb-8 text-white">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" class="lucide lucide-layout">
                  <rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2"></rect>
                  <path d="M3 9h18"></path>
                  <path d="M9 21V9"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-[#965228] font-medium mb-3">Web Design</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">Interfacce Intuitive</h3>
              <p class="opacity-70 leading-relaxed">
                Siti web che non sono solo vetrine, ma strumenti di conversione progettati per guidare l'utente con naturalezza e precisione.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article
              class="bg-[#F7F3EB] p-10 rounded-3xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl group border border-transparent hover:border-[#824D5E]/20"
              data-aos="fade-up"
              data-aos-delay="200"
            >
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#3B2132] to-[#824D5E] flex items-center justify-center mb-8 text-white">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" class="lucide lucide-cpu">
                  <path d="M12 20v2"></path>
                  <path d="M12 2v2"></path>
                  <path d="M17 20v2"></path>
                  <path d="M17 2v2"></path>
                  <path d="M2 12h2"></path>
                  <path d="M2 17h2"></path>
                  <path d="M2 7h2"></path>
                  <path d="M20 12h2"></path>
                  <path d="M20 17h2"></path>
                  <path d="M20 7h2"></path>
                  <path d="M7 20v2"></path>
                  <path d="M7 2v2"></path>
                  <rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2"></rect>
                  <rect x="8" y="8" width="8" height="8" rx="1"></rect>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-[#965228] font-medium mb-3">AI Software</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">Automazione Intelligente</h3>
              <p class="opacity-70 leading-relaxed">
                Sviluppiamo software custom che integrano l'AI per eliminare i task ripetitivi e ottimizzare i flussi di lavoro aziendali.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article
              class="bg-[#F7F3EB] p-10 rounded-3xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl group border border-transparent hover:border-[#824D5E]/20"
              data-aos="fade-up"
              data-aos-delay="300"
            >
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#3B2132] to-[#824D5E] flex items-center justify-center mb-8 text-white">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" class="lucide lucide-zap">
                  <path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-[#965228] font-medium mb-3">Process Optimization</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">Ingegneria dei Processi</h3>
              <p class="opacity-70 leading-relaxed">
                Analizziamo il tuo business per mappare i colli di bottiglia e risolverli con soluzioni tecnologiche su misura.
              </p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="vision" class="py-24 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="relative" data-aos="fade-right">
            <img
              src="https://loremflickr.com/600/800/paper,desk"
              alt="Tavolo da lavoro con schizzi e tecnologia"
              class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover"
            />
            <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-48 h-48 bg-[#00A5B5] rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-20"></div>
          </div>
          <div data-aos="fade-left">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif mb-6">
              Tecnologia che <br />
              <em class="text-[#1F5867]">si adatta all'uomo</em>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg opacity-80 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
              Crediamo che l'AI non debba sostituire l'intelligenza umana, ma potenziarla. Il nostro approccio è
              <strong>antropocentrico</strong>: creiamo strumenti che semplificano la burocrazia digitale per restituire alle persone ciò che conta davvero: la creatività e la strategia.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                <div class="mt-1 text-[#00A5B5]">
